        {
            "title": "金融圈多位大佬不約而同示警 私人信貸市場風險升高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Mark Coombs攝影：Ore Huiying/彭博社\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IRGqPq2wtJqEmWGrmRy4OQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/48adcacb06bb3905d5b3d8a70a343ace\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Mark Coombs攝影：Ore Huiying/彭博社</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 金融圈的億萬富豪們不約而同擔心私人市場的風險日益升高；他們認為，資產估值大幅上漲、監管不力以及宏觀經濟壓力是這種風險升高的原因。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Nu Holdings Ltd.聯合創始人David Vélez本周在新加坡舉行的彭博創新經濟論壇間隙接受彭博電視台採訪時表示，私人市場存在一些泡沫。這位哥倫比亞大亨表示，「我確信這個領域會出現一些糟糕的投資，我們且拭​​目以待。」他還補充說，資訊揭露方面的監管不力也加劇了風險。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bc02c538-1072-3c96-91a6-4f93bd97ccbb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"David Vélez攝影：Ore Huiying/彭博社\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9dHaNJdNisP.YT93ODFe2Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b4e68fa42aaec7f0545b4c9ac5a7ea34\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">David Vélez攝影：Ore Huiying/彭博社</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些評論讓外界更加擔心，近期在美國一些引發關注的破產事件可能意味著金融體系中更廣泛的信貸問題。人們也越來越擔心，規模達1.7萬億美元的私人信貸行業可能會為金融體系帶來新的複雜性和風險。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通執行長傑米‧戴蒙在上個月表示，當你看到一隻蟑螂時，很可能還有更多。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國億萬富豪、Ashmore Group Plc執行長Mark Coombs周四在新加坡的活動上表示，「我看到蟑螂時，我會尖叫逃跑，這大概就是我對發達市場私人信貸的看法吧。」這家資產管理公司的資產規模達500億英鎊（650億美元）。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Marc Rowan攝影師：Lionel Ng/彭博社\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ubtPZA53XtRehG6_Tx22sg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/45f705e23b476156b936c7a585526c73\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Marc Rowan攝影師：Lionel Ng/彭博社</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">億萬富豪、阿波羅全球管理執行長Marc Rowan在同一論壇指出，投資人或許應該透過提升信用等級來「降低風險」。他表示，資產價格並不便宜，長期利率可能維持高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Finance Billionaires Warn of Rising Private Credit Market Risks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Haslinda Amin、Francine Lacqua、Joanne Wong.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
